{"type":"message","id":"584f212b","parentId":"1dc880d5","timestamp":"2026-02-27T09:38:06.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了：\n\n1. **批注 JS 使用相对路径**：\n   - `apiBase: ''` - 默认使用相对路径\n   - `fetch('/api/annotations')` - 会请求 `https://kuroneko.chat/api/annotations`\n\n2. **Nginx 配置有两个路由**：\n   - `/api/annotations` → 批注 API（3002 端口）\n   - `/abyss/api/` → 批注 API（3002 端口）\n\n3. **小说阅读页面 URL**：\n   - **目录页**：`https://kuroneko.chat/novel/abyss/`\n   - **章节页**：`https://kuroneko.chat/novel/abyss/chapters/1.html`（支持批注）\n   - **交互式阅读器**：`https://kuroneko.chat/novel/abyss/reader.html`（支持批注）\n\n4. **批注功能**：\n   - ✅ 章节页面已引入批注 JS\n   - ✅ 批注 API 服务正常运行\n   - ✅ Nginx 已配置代理\n   - ✅ **批注功能可用**\n\n让我验证一下外部访问是否正常。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_69f8614220e4467f9ef85c42","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://kuroneko.chat/api/annotations?chapter=1 2>/dev/null | head -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc244ee4bc7b420c81d5f5d8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://kuroneko.chat/novel/abyss/chapters/1.html 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"annotation-selector|批注\" | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":466,"output":342,"cacheRead":52544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53352,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772185071241}}
